[07/11/2017 11:05:56] <font color="#ff00ff">Ya.</font>
[07/11/2017 11:06:00] <font color="#00ff00">Vale.</font>
[07/11/2017 11:06:04] <font color="#00ff00">No se trata únicamente de eso,</font>
[07/11/2017 11:06:04] <font color="#00ff00">sin querer...</font>
